The Suicidal Princes are the very newest forums , sweeping the nation! Already, we have members such as
Pwnd, and Freddy1990 joined!
A Growing community, already great. A well-known global moderator known as 2pure4u on these forums, Darkwaverose on mine. A great GFX'er Named Blake, Co-Owner of the forums. Then me, The founder, owner, and site creator! You may ask me:
What does these forums have to offer me that I don't already have?
Well, just to list a few!
[ul][li]A chill place, just to hang out Fun Admins and Mods (not that this place doesnt have fun admins and mods) 1 more open global moderator position Introduction thread, made to feel you welcome ;) The nicest people you will EVER meet A Chatbox, which is a cool chatroom at the bottom of the forums, just like an instant messenger! And some members such as Pwnd, 2pure4u, And Freddy1990![/li][/ul]
So why don't you come on down and register, have yourself a good time!
